Omotayo Edubi Actress and mother of three, Mercy Johnson used her Instagram handle to announce the death of her mother. She requested for her privacy and that of her family as they mourn their tragic loss, she said that her family would appreciate prayers from fans and friends to deal with the trying time they are facing, the cause of the death was not mentioned. “It deeply saddens me to say that my beloved mother is gone. This is a trying time for my family and we would appreciate your prayers, even as we plead for our privacy at this time. Thank you.”